5. The Learning Path: Beginner â†’ Builder

The Stacks program focuses on progressive onboarding, so users start easy and gradually move toward hands-on creation.

Stage 1: Beginner missions

Learn what Stacks is

Install a wallet

Interact with a Stacks website

Follow Stacks channels

Stage 2: Intermediate missions

Sign transactions

Explore smart contract documentation

Learn about Clarinet and Stacks.js

Stage 3: Builder missions

Write your first Clarity contract

Deploy a local devnet app

Use Testnet tools

This structure transforms passive learners into real contributors inside the Stacks ecosystem.
